data: Define, lengthen and nourish lashes with organic shea butter, grapeseed and jojoba oils. Lashes are coated gently and evenly without clumping, transferring or flaking. Long, lush lashes begin with this luxe mascara that is formulated with organic shea butter and oils of grape and jojoba seed to help nourish and condition as it lengthens and defines. Velvety and smooth, it coats lashes gently and evenly without clumping, transferring, or flaking. Made for Young Delicate Skin Types.
